title: Air Releases (AIRS/AFS) for Washington DC
name: Air Releases (AIRS/AFS) for Washington DC
description:
Air Emission locations. The dataset contains locations and attributes of Air Emissions, created as part of the DC Geographic Information System (DC GIS) for the D.C. Office of the Chief Technology Officer (OCTO) and participating D.C. government agencies.

A database provided by the Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) identified Air Emission locations. All DC GIS data is stored and exported in Maryland State Plane coordinates NAD 83 meters.
